<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Your planning application</h1>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      <strong>At:</strong> <%= @planning_application.full_address %> <br>
      <strong>Date received:</strong> <%= @planning_application.date_received %> <br>
      <strong>Application number: </strong>@planning_application.reference <br>
      <br>
    </p>
    <p class="govuk-body">
      The case officer working on your application has requested changes to your planning application.
    </p>
    <div class="govuk-inset-text">
      <p class="govuk-body">
        If requested changes are not received within 15 working days, by the <strong>REQUEST_FOR_CHANGE_EXPIRY_HERE</strong>
        your application will be returned and your payment refunded.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="govuk-heading-s">What you need to do:</p>
    <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
      <li>Each link below requires a separate action.</li>
      <li>Click on each link to see what action is required.</li>
      <li>Once you have submitted an action, you can no longer make changes to it. The status for that action will change to completed. </li>
      <li>You need to complete all actions before your case officer can proceed with your planning application.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="govuk-body">Where additional information or documents have been requested
      you will have the opportunity to disagree with the request. However it will take <strong> 15 days</strong> for the
      planning officer to process your request and review new changes. </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-summary-list">
    <div class="govuk-summary-list__row">
      <ol class="app-task-list">
        <li>
          <h2 class="app-task-list__section">
            <span class="app-task-list__section-number">1. </span> Confirm changes to your application description
          </h2>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <ul class="app-task-list__items" id="validation-section">
        <% @change_requests["data"].each do |change_request| %>
          <li class="app-task-list__item">
            <span class="app-task-list__task-name">
              <% if change_request["type"] == "description_change_request" %>
                Description
              <% end %>
            </span>
            <strong class="govuk-tag app-task-list__tag" id="eligibility-status">
              <% if change_request["state"] == 'open' %>
                Not started
              <% else %>
                Complete
              <% end %>
            </strong>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



